---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Community">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8 text-slate-900">Community</h1>
  <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">
    Community features are under development. Here is what we are building.
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Contributing</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
        We are building a contribution system for peer-reviewed content. When complete, you will be
        able to:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Suggest corrections to articles</li>
        <li>Add citations and references</li>
        <li>Create new flashcards and quiz questions</li>
        <li>Translate content to other languages</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Quality Standards</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">All content follows these standards:</p>
      <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Peer-reviewed sources with DOI citations</li>
        <li>IUPAC nomenclature for chemical names</li>
        <li>Molecular formulas and weight verification</li>
        <li>Fact-checking by domain experts</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 p-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Get Involved</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
      This is an open educational project. If you have expertise in peptide biology, biochemistry,
      or pharmacology, we welcome your contributions. The content pipeline is designed for accuracy
      and reproducibility.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
      Content is authored in Markdown with structured frontmatter. All articles undergo schema
      validation and automated testing before deployment.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
